      <title>财新PMI显示2月份中国服务业活动增长势头减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-feb-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二的一项私营部门调查显示，中国 2 月份服务业活动增长放缓，商业信心连续第二个月放缓，企业自 11 月份以来首次裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-feb-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
